OL,3,CDaniel Khalife tells court he
OL,4,C'considered travelling to Iran'
OL,6,FFormer British soldier, Daniel
OL,7,FKhalife, who is accused of passing
OL,8,Fsecret information to Iran, considered
OL,9,Ftravelling to the Middle Eastern
OL,10,Fcountry before deciding it would be
OL,11,Ftoo "dangerous," Woolwich Crown Court
OL,12,Fheard today.
OL,14,FGiving evidence at the court, Daniel
OL,15,FKhalife said he wanted to "draw out"
OL,16,Fthe Iranian intelligence officers he
OL,17,Fwas in touch with and "strengthen the
OL,18,Frelationship based on lies".
