OL,3,CDaniel Khalife tells court he
OL,4,C'considered travelling to Iran'
OL,6,FThe 23-year-old told jurors he
OL,7,F"considered potentially travelling to
OL,8,FIran" while still a serving soldier,
OL,9,Fbut feared there could be consequences
OL,10,Fif they found out the information he
OL,11,Fwas providing was "fictitious".
OL,13,F"I felt this would be dangerous," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FWhen police arrested him and searched
OL,17,Fhis room, they found a number of
OL,18,F"completely fake" documents purporting
OL,19,Fto be from MPs, senior military
OL,20,Fofficials and the security services,
OL,21,Fhis trial heard previously.
