OL,3,CDaniel Khalife tells court he
OL,4,C'considered travelling to Iran'
OL,6,FKhalife told the court he thought up a
OL,7,Fplan to "digitise" the documents, by
OL,8,Fputting a laptop in a "fake diplomatic
OL,9,Fbag" to make it seem like it had been
OL,10,Fintercepted.
OL,12,FHe intended to try and sell the
OL,13,Fdevice, jurors heard.
OL,15,FAsked about the use of WhatsApp groups
OL,16,Fto share orders and even secret
OL,17,Fdocuments in the army, Khalife said
OL,18,Fthe practice was "standard procedure",
OL,19,Fadding that it would be "impossible"
OL,20,Fto operate without it.
