OL,3,CDaniel Khalife tells court he
OL,4,C'considered travelling to Iran'
OL,6,FThe former soldier is alleged to have
OL,7,Ffled his army barracks in January 2023
OL,8,Fwhen he realised he would face
OL,9,Fcriminal charges over allegations he
OL,10,Fpassed classified information to
OL,11,FIran's intelligence service.
OL,13,FLater, while on remand, he is alleged
OL,14,Fto have escaped from HMP Wandsworth in
OL,15,FSeptember 2023 by tying himself to the
OL,16,Funderside of a food delivery truck
OL,17,Fusing bedsheets.
