OL,3,CDaniel Khalife tells court he
OL,4,C'considered travelling to Iran'
OL,6,FAs well as the prison escape, he also
OL,7,Ffaces charges contrary to the Official
OL,8,FSecrets Act and Terrorism Act, and is
OL,9,Faccused of perpetrating a bomb hoax.
OL,11,FHe denies all the charges, and the
OL,12,Ftrial continues.
